						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1329 (1407 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers the gift of cows towards maintaining a lamp and milk offerings to the god and goddess, by Raṅgaṇa-Uḍaiyar, son of <hi rend="italic">Mahāpradhāni</hi> Jembaya-Deṇṇāyakkar. The record is dated in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1329, Sarvajit, Aṟpaśi 7,</hi> probably corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1407, October 6.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
